data.description: Come and see!! This newly updated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home!! Beautiful updated kitchen, barn style doors, with master bedroom and master bathroom upstairs.  New roof, and newly installed windows will be coming soon. This beauty has a detached garage with efficiency apartment. The apartment has 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, living area and kitchenette.  Large privacy, fenced backyard with plenty of room for a future pool, or lots of room for the kids and pets to play.  Don't miss out on this amazing home in a wonderful neighborhood! Won't last long!
